longBusinessSummary: Athanase Innovation AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, operates as an alternative investment firm in Sweden. The company invests in private and public technology and innovation companies. It also develops and sells machine vision inspection systems, such as the Ivisys Pallet AI for automated pallet inspection. Athanase Innovation AB (publ) was founded in 2016 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
